data.description: Nestled in the sought-after community of Key Haven, this home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing comfort and space. The entire house has central AC. The large family room creates a welcoming ambiance, perfect for relaxing with family and friends or hosting gatherings. The terrazzo floors offer durability and easy maintenance. Convenience is a top priority with off-street parking available, ensuring that you and your guests always have a designated spot. The property boasts a large concrete dock, allowing you to moor your boat or simply relax by the water's edge. With easy access to both the Gulf of Mexico and the Atlantic Ocean, you'll have the freedom to explore and enjoy all that the surrounding waterways have to offer. For those seeking outdoor enjoyment, this property provides ample space for a pool, creating a private oasis where you can cool off and unwind.
